data.description: Get away from the city and relax outdoors. This fully fenced property offers plenty of outdoor space for activities including an above ground poor and corals for animals. The home has been beautifully maintained and has enough space for family and friends. A large covered patio offers great space for entertaining outdoors and a full sized detached garage offers a great space for a workshop.This lot is one of the very few level landscapes in the area. Come enjoy the beautiful scenery and wildlife Coulterville has to offer.
